&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Use data-oriented approaches to identify potential areas of improvement within the business, with a specific focus on asset support&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt; Partner with compliance, legal, and development teams to deliver products in-line with a consistent asset strategy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
