&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About Digital Asset&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Digital Asset helps companies of all sizes and across industries get distributed applications to market faster, and stay there longer. At the core of our service offering is DAML (daml.com), the open source and platform-independent smart contract framework that enables developers to write an application once and deploy it anywhere. Today, we work with some of the largest companies in the world to harness the transformative power of smart contracts - a component of the distributed ledger technology (DLT) stack - and change the way applications are developed, deployed and used to solve real-world business challenges.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Digital Asset is a global company with offices in New York, London, Budapest, Zurich, Hong Kong, and Sydney.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As we grow our team, we will maintain the dynamic, collaborative and pragmatic way of working that has grounded our efforts from the beginning.&amp;nbsp; If you seek to develop solutions others have yet to contemplate, this opportunity may be right for you!&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Opportunity&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Digital Asset (DA) is looking for an experienced and creative Global Recruitment Manager who thrives in a fast-paced and entrepreneurial environment.&amp;nbsp; Under the direction of the Director of Human Resources, the Global Recruitment Manager is responsible for managing the recruitment process and team (both direct and indirect), and for sourcing and selecting qualified candidates domestically and internationally for DA.&amp;nbsp; In view of the highly technical nature of recruitment in a variety of subject areas, the Global Recruitment Manager will collaborate closely with executives and directors of each of our functional areas.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop global recruitment systems, policies, procedures, tools and templates to ensure streamlined, effective, and high quality services are delivered, with regular recruitment metrics and reporting on progress.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Develop and recommend global recruitment strategies to ensure successful searches.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Maintain the firm’s ATS (Greenhouse) and guide effective use by hiring managers, interviewers, etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Identify potential candidates through direct sourcing, job boards, databases, contacts/networks, and external agencies.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Mentor and coach DA managers and key staff in recruitment procedures and best practices.&amp;nbsp; Conduct regular interviewer training.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Facilitate candidate debrief meetings with hiring managers and interviewers, and model evidence-based selection decision-making.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Manage the firm’s relationships with external agencies, providing guidance and feedback, and ensuring that we get quality candidates that meet our job specifications.&amp;nbsp; Keeping agency fees under control is a key aspect of the Global Recruitment Manager’s role.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Play an active leadership role in the firm’s Diversity, Equity &amp;amp; Inclusion programs and initiatives.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Participate in building the positive employer brand for DA -- work with Marketing &amp;amp; Communications on specific initiatives; attend conferences, career fairs, and special events when they support the firm’s strategic plans; etc.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Conduct reference checks, as needed, for potential hires into key roles.&amp;nbsp; Extend employment offers, support salary negotiations, and help close candidates where needed.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Maintain the firm’s library of job specifications/hiring plans; understand and support visa considerations; and complete other duties, as assigned.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key Criteria&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;10+ years previous recruitment experience, in a fast-paced environment&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Business Administration, Human Resources Management or related field.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Strong ability to source candidates directly and to qualify them against job requirements; interest in implementing new sourcing methods and innovating on hiring practices by using new methods or channels.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Experience using time management skills, such as prioritizing/organizing and tracking details or meeting deadlines of multiple projects with varying target fill dates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Ability to work well under pressure and in a fast-paced and dynamic environment, with a high degree of accuracy and attention to detail.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Understanding of and commitment to driving diversity throughout the hiring process.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
