&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;As a Software Engineer on the Circle team, you will build scalable microservices that are responsible for reliable and secure APIs that transfer value &amp;amp; assets across all blockchain protocols (think Bitcoin and Ethereum, for example) as well as traditional banking protocols (think credit cards, bank transfers etc).&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
